        "TileImage": "$($repository fd5e4b5f-ade1-4323-8622-823b48685b9f).Image",
        "Description": "Good Evening, 47. Your targets today are Jackie and Julian Carrington. Jackie is well known for her leading role in hit sitcom &quot;Acquaintances&quot; but she is also known for severely abusing the cast and crew. In fact, the suicide on set that ended up cancelling the show was her doing, and numerous others. Julian was a cameraman on &quot;Acquaintances&quot; but once it ended, he started working for the band &quot;The Class&quot; He is an accomplice to Jackie and once murdered a crew member from &quot;The Class&quot; Good Luck, 47",
